# Local dev: leave empty so the app is served at http://localhost:5173/
# GitHub Pages: set to "/<repo-name>/" (trailing slash). Example for this project:
# VITE_BASE_PATH=/software-subscription-tracker/
#
# If this is set in your system environment, local URLs look like
# http://localhost:5173/software-subscription-tracker/ — unset for plain "/".
# VITE_BASE_PATH=
#
# Playwright E2E uses `npm run dev:e2e` (empty base) so http://localhost:5173/ works.
